## Migrations
{{- if .HasProfile}}
**Tool: {{.Profile.DB.Migrations}}**

Rules:
- Migrations are **always forward-only** — no rollback scripts
- Each migration must be atomic (single transaction where possible)
- Never modify an existing migration file — add a new one
- Migration filenames: `{timestamp}_{description}.up.sql`
